{% set title = 'LTO Network - Use case - ScanTrust' %}
{% set description = 'The revival of the QR-Code with Blockchain' %}

{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block content %}

<div class="section-container">
  <section class="hero is-medium" style="background-image: url(/assets/slider-image-car@3x.png);">
    <div class="hero-body">
      <div class="container">
          <div class=""><span class="tag is-rounded is-medium blue-grey"> INTEGRATOR </span></div>
        <h1 class="primary-text">Validation-as-a-service (VaaS)</h1>
          <h2 class="dark-indigo">Enabling brands with smart packaging solutions for product authentication, supply chain traceability and consumer engagement on blockchain.</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutout-top">
  <section class="section secondary no-padding">
    <div class="promo-numbers c">
      <div class="container use-cases">
        <div class="item use-cases">
            <p class="promo-head use-cases">Client</p>
            <img class="promo-client" src="/assets/use-cases/scantrust@2x.png">
        </div>
        <div class="item use-cases">
            <p class="promo-head use-cases">Involved parties</p>
          <p class="promo-desc use-cases muted">ScanTrust delivers their smart QR-code services to the world’s largest companies, such as ExxonMobil, Unilever, Shell and AB InBev.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutin-top-alt cutout-bottom">
    <section class="section">

  <div class="advantages-div">
    <div class="advantages-title-container container">
      <h2 class="deep-lavender">Integrator overview</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="advantages-content-container">

      <div class="columns advantages">
        <div class="column advantages image left-side">
          <div class="advantages left-side column-subdiv">
            <img src="/assets/rocks/rock-1.svg" class="rock-tree">
            <img id="advantages-small-rock-1" src="/assets/small-rock-1.svg">
            <img id="advantages-small-rock-2" src="/assets/small-rock-2.svg">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column advantages is-two-thirds right-side">
          <div class="advantages-text-container right-side">
            <h3 class="title dark-indigo advantages">The problem</h3>
              <div class="content">
            <p class="muted">Every supply chain, regardless of industry, has common pain points that plague the entire system such as volatility of demand, talent shortage, and rising commodity prices. Unfortunately, these issues don't have simple answers and will likely always require constant vigilance due to the inherent nature of supply chains.</p>
                  <p class="muted">There are other often more problematic pain points supply chains face such as little-to-no transparency, low quality data, and the ever-present danger of counterfeits.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="columns advantages">
        <div class="column advantages image left-side">
          <div class="advantages left-side column-subdiv">
            <img src="/assets/rocks/rock-2.svg" class="rock-rocket">
            <img id="advantages-small-rock-3" src="/assets/small-rock-3.svg">
            <img id="advantages-small-rock-4" src="/assets/small-rock-4.svg">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column advantages is-two-thirds right-side">
          <div class="advantages-text-container right-side">
            <h3 class="title dark-indigo advantages">Solution</h3>
              <div class="content">
                  <p class="muted">Enhancing product transparency and increase consumer trust using ScanTrust's Blockchain connectors. Key product information can be made public on the blockchain and once stored, data cannot be altered or deleted.</p>
                  </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


    </div>

    <table class="table advantages has-margin-top-40">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="dark-indigo" colspan="2">Theme</th>
          <th class="dark-indigo" colspan="2">LTO Network solution</th>
          <th class="dark-indigo" colspan="2">Traditional solution</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>

      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="deep-lavender">Immutability</th>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-checkmark" src="/assets/table icon - good.svg"> </td>
          <td class="steel">Anchoring (data related to) smart QR codes allows for utmost trust in the sender and the provenance data.</td>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-x" src="/assets/table icon - bad.svg"></td>
          <td class="steel">Smart QR-codes can be linked to a piece of information that hasn’t been properly validated.</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="deep-lavender">Supply chains</th>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-checkmark" src="/assets/table icon - good.svg"> </td>
          <td class="steel">Using LTO Network’s decentralized workflows, data behind the QR codes can be efficiently exchanged over stakeholder systems.</td>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-x" src="/assets/table icon - bad.svg"></td>
          <td class="steel">Data captured in the Smart-QR code needs to be re-entered at every stakeholder in the supply chain.</td>
        </tr>


        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="deep-lavender">Costs / Speed of anchoring</th>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-checkmark" src="/assets/table icon - good.svg"> </td>
          <td class="steel">LTO’s blockchain is optimized for anchoring, making transactions near-instant and affordable.</td>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-x" src="/assets/table icon - bad.svg"></td>
          <td class="steel">Traditional blockchains tend to be very slow and expensive to anchor this many transactions.</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
        </tr>
      </tbody>

    </table>

    <div class="btn-container has-text-centered">
    <a href="#" class="button is-primary" target="blank">
      Learn more
    </a>
</div>
  </div>
</section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutout-bottom-alt">
  <section class="section alt p-top-l">
<div class="container">
        <div class="columns is-centered">
            <div class="column is-three-fifths has-text-centered video">
                <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/Zs17a4cDcU4?controls=0" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="btn-container has-text-centered has-margin-top-40">
    <a href="#" target="blank" class="button is-primary">Request a demo</a>
  </div>
        </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container">
  <section class="section relative tertiary p-top-l neg-m-top-m ecosystem-v">
      <div class="section-body">
        <div class="ecosystem-v"></div>
        <div class="columns is-mobile">
        <div class="column is-4 is-offset-8">
            <h2 class="section-title">Ecosystem V</h2>
            <div class="content">
                <p class="muted">We amplify growth by sharing incentives on the same principles behind blockchain. We leverage our connections and those of other Ecosystem V members who benefit from continuous support and development through our community of hundreds of developers and ecosystem participants.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="button is-rounded is-primary main-button use-cases">Learn more</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutout-top cutout-bottom-alt">
  <section class="section p-top-xl p-bottom-xl alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="columns is-centered">
        <div class="column is-half">
            <blockquote>Blockchain is a technology that can clearly augment our solution and has tremendous potential for the supply chain space. When we researched blockchain platforms, LTO Network stood out in terms of speed, set-up, and capabilities. We are able to include the blockchain transaction identifier directly into our scanning logs which are circulated upon scanning, without the need to wait minutes for confirmations. Next to that, the Live Contract features that LTO Network offers can be very interesting for our enterprise customers in the long-run.
                <div class="author">Nathan Anderson, CEO ScanTrust</div>
            </blockquote>
        </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container">
  <section class="section alt has-bg-img" style="background-image: url('/assets/bot-image@3x.png')">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column card">
          <img class="card-rock-image" src="/assets/rocks/card-rock-1.svg">
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3 class="accent-text has-text-centered">Developer area</h3>
            <div class="card-description has-text-centered">
              <p>Get to know the tech, set up a node and learn how to build your first product or integration on LTO network.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-action centered">
              <a href="#" class="button is-primary">
                Learn more
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="column card">
          <img class="card-rock-image" src="/assets/rocks/card-rock-2.svg">
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3 class="accent-text has-text-centered">Community area</h3>
            <div class="card-description has-text-centered">
              <p>Ready to put your marketing, design and development skills into practice? Join the community!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-action centered">
              <a href="#" class="button is-primary">
                Learn more
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="column card">
          <img class="card-rock-image" src="/assets/rocks/card-rock-3.svg">
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3 class="accent-text has-text-centered">Contact us</h3>
            <div class="card-description has-text-centered">
              <p>Got a question on implementing blockchain in your (clients) organization? The LTO Network team is here to help you out!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-action centered">
              <a href="#" class="button is-primary">
                Learn more
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

{% endblock %}
